* The agent assist tools and knowledge management systems segment is anticipated to grow at the fastest CAGR during the forecast period.

## End Use Insights
* The BFSI segment accounted for the largest market revenue share in 2024.
* The retail and e-commerce segment is rapidly expanding its use of AI to enhance customer engagement.

## Regional Insights
* North America dominated the AI for customer service market with the largest revenue share of 37.2% in 2024.
